name: Facing Metropolitan
description:
Everyone struggles to live where they live. Living in a big city like Jakarta is the hope of most Indonesians. Because they think they have more opportunities to survive and earn an income. But in reality it is not always so, some succeed there are also those who fail. What else can we do but keep struggling?


This photo is unpossed. I took this photo on the street of Jakarta, Indonesia in 2017.
